Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ 誰が告げるのか悲嘆の果て失うもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 有誰能宣告 悲嘆的盡頭所失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托利君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三河君主 赫萊森.阿里亞達斯特現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,440)\fs22}Ariadust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了武藏阿里亞達斯特教導院的入學推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,440)\fs22}Ariadust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的人身安全將由武藏阿里亞達斯特教導院的學生會和總長連合保護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,440)\fs22}Westfalen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將今後全部的抗爭的和談交予之後的威斯特法倫會議定奪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,392)}{\fn方正粗宋_GBK}{\4c&H0F0F0F&}{\3c&H0F0F0F&}{\bord1\fad(650,700)}『境界線上的整列者們』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托利大人 就情況來看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以判斷奪回另一個大罪武裝是不太可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊 不能讓你「淫亂」了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有搞錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說時間到了 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 公主的入學推薦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到家之前都算遠足 這個你們忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到武藏之前受理都無效啊 笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這豈不是很糟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 再來一次 One chance！！One chance！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輪到吾輩的戲份了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,減少水分 加強硬度 我上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稔侍 Good！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮光丸 在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦長和學長們說要自己去追
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把年輕人都丟下？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖下 借您的船一用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs22}舊派：聖譜獨奏舊派 K.P.A.意大利等信仰的聖譜Tsirhc系教譜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,440)\fs22}Italia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要聖下健在 K.P.A.意大利及舊派就不算敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇決不能威信掃地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論何時都該輝煌閃耀 舊派才能保住這不斷的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借您的船一用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有榮光丸和我這條命在 就可以判斷能夠阻止武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有歸還的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(184,440)\fs22}Tes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,440)\fs22}Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 身為舊派 此身此魂只要是獻於聖譜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝等將銘刻于時代 而吾則確保歷史不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,440)\fs22}Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都遵循聖譜的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勞您費心 感激之至
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過那載重的運輸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近武藏直到公主從運輸艦下來  用流體砲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連結吧 「蜻蜓切」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣撞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓船靠過去 我再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 沒法繼續割斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 阿里亞達斯特同學在？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此 有何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收大罪武裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砲擊的同時撞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,440)\fs22}Italia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了舊派和K.P.A.意大利 以及教皇總長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與不斷之光輝同在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大罪武裝「悲嘆的怠惰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托利 「悲嘆的怠惰」被壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就頂回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出疑問 為什麼開始揉捏赫萊森的屁股呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自動人偶的赫萊森的靈魂啟動方式從來沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫萊森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸掉 落敗 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫萊森 安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我葵托利 就在這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌唱吧 赫萊森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了通行的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員退避!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的感情 為什麼如此 如此的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧 赫萊森
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將痛苦的感情釋放出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將全部奪回來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩下很多很多高興的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就趁還沒奪回的現在享受這份痛楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不能哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就替我哭泣吧 呐喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有悲傷的味道啊 赫萊森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 能將其它滋味也告訴身處此處的我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去奪回吧 你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將一切羈絆於你的大罪 聚集在你我的境界線上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 終有一日 終有一日定會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵從所有的感情與我一起歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫萊森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束…了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 現在才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走這邊 回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 武藏野在搞慶典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚鬧鬧也無妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來大叔我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對真喜子的經歷有點興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒什麼出眾的經歷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我班上的孩子們更轟轟烈烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如托利的家世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,440)\fs22}Ariadust
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵家本來是阿里亞達斯特家的護衛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那都是經歷不明的部分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是神秘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學院長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是二鏡紋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由武藏通報全艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空戰艦一艘 正從右舷上空通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,440)\fs22}Emblem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.A.ODA的紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是織田的鐵甲艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是P.A.ODA的五大頂之首——柴田勝家的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是航線重疊造成的失誤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是來打招呼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.A.ODA的五大頂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也被稱為六天魔軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管我方使用了隱形航行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.A.ODA也能夠解析出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這種意思的示威行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please kill me all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生的制服總覺得有些不習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 有什麼打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 東側航路不管哪裡都是敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連隱形航行都可能被發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能去江戶了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從正在與聖連抗爭中的P.A.ODA方面穿過向北也不是好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是向西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我是在詢問你個人的打算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼還是說說我們今後的打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來我們去的地方是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要去的是英國
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英國…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始為了未來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要和英國取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃前往出雲進行武藏的補給維修等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事這麼喧鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個工口遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人果然還是要負責金髮巨乳路線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼貧僧本次就負責御姐路線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御廣敷負責攻略蘿莉角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 小生不是蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對年輕的生命力的崇尚 是生命禮讚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀哦呀 稔侍君的臉好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒法喝賞月美酒實在遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是紅酒咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴同學 需要取什麼吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經吃得很飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿伽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪歌特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持槍的本多同學 你的轉學文件有6處錯字漏字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然收購費用水漲船高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部分的話之前的貿易中已經賺過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊幹嘛啊你們 在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還準備了這麼多大盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是慶典 慶典啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛的景緻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要幫你化妝喲 做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 平常不是老在嚷嚷會胖都不吃麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是慶功會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說今天做了那麼多運動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 正純同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是給我們家孩子很高的評價真是萬分感謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣被你鄭重其事道出事實真讓人沮喪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 葵和赫萊森呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正純 小聲一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人好像都睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺還在摸大腿啊 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫萊森的靈魂所記得的歌…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都將從明天開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是明天的早晨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫萊森說要給愚弟做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次會是兩個人一起吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人都說難吃的話 她會露出怎樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上要儘量不遲到才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我三征西班牙總長連合學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定將第一特務的同時襲名——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加西亞.德.塞巴留斯和立花宗茂中的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立花宗茂的襲名解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗茂大人將不再是宗茂大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副會長 請允許我出戰前線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該比你的夫君立花宗茂更弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,440)\fs22}Tes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(464,440)\fs22}Ariadust
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我若能成為打倒武藏阿里亞達斯特教導院的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能證明比我更強的第一特務的敗北 僅僅是陰差陽錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西側的天空上貌似感知到武藏的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這好像是三征西班牙的…船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒! 三征西班牙的攻擊艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(268,440)\fs22}Kraken
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,440)\fs22}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫拉肯級兩艘和雙足飛龍級六艘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正於奧多摩上空 大約五百米處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,440)\fs22}Tres Espana              Kraken
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認三征西班牙的庫拉肯級開始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落預計到達時間為3分12秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方 已公告了此襲擊的大義名分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三征西班牙的領域中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕獲準備給英國運載補充物資的船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的降下數目 推測大概200人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是入侵而是襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們挺住對方的攻擊就能結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣說也沒關係哦 「打贏他們」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了 敵人打頭陣的是三征西班牙的田徑隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,On your mark！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Get set！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝哦八艘！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員投擲!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,440)\fs22}Tres Espana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…三征西班牙的「四死球」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩特羅和弗洛雷斯的瓦爾迪斯兄妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒吧 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 魔球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,440)\fs22}Container
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 告訴我大型木箱的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(464,440)\fs22}Szwarc Floren
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上咯 「黑孃」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們前往村山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 地摺朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 東
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下參上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們見識一下吧 人生送終安打
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下 流體能源儲存預備池中解放百分之十二
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力航行 補充準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本艦進行變型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三分後 將移動到重力航行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力脫離本空域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 武藏一方的各位請一定要頂住戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈咦？
